    Black Aracniascreams with such rage one of the computer monitors falls to 
the floor. With the keyboard she shut the hatch, (which wasnt open and you 
really should check next time instead of the elaborate mode you just did.) 
and sealed the four Maximals in the ship.
    "Now, they will pay for there actions! Examples must be made of them. 
Computer, activate a force feild around sector 9 in the main corridor in 
front of the hatch. That will contain them." She hissed, glareing at her 
scanners and diagnostics.
    The computer did so, and trapped the four maximals in the sector. Then, 
with the command from Aracnia, the Nerve gas was pumped inside the force 
feild where the Maximals were. And, to flavor there death, Aracnia started 
the internal autoguns that began to fire apon them.
    "Now that they will be dead in minutes, I want Paralysis and Darkmouse to 
go stand gaurd by them. Quickstrike and THunder Hammer should go to. I'll 
send Mosquitor shortly. But, above all, I WANT THEM DEAD!" She screamed.
